# Keep the Docker build context small.
# Anything excluded here cannot be COPY'd by the Dockerfile.

# Source / build tooling not needed at runtime
program/
tribes_data/
anchor_studio/
docs/
comms/
*.md

# Bulk source data we don't need at runtime: 230 MB of .fbx raw inputs +
# unused .glb characters. The renderer only loads wolf_sentinel.glb.
assets/models/*
!assets/models/wolf_sentinel.glb

# These were over-aggressively excluded before and broke renderer.js.
# All of buildings/, weapons/, audio/, hdri/ are genuinely loaded at runtime.
# So: keep them in.

# Dev artefacts
.git/
.github/
.vscode/
*.log
node_modules/
server/node_modules/
*.tar.gz
*.zip
*.blend

# Keep the Dockerfile itself out of the image
# (Docker build context still needs them so they're commented out.)
# Dockerfile
# .dockerignore
# fly.toml
